node.text:
Repost from @evolurbaby using @RepostRegramApp - “I’m on baby number 3 and so blessed to be able to have a healthy supply for my babies. I didn’t know what I was doing or what to expect with my firstborn... but it came so naturally and I breastfeed my son until he was 2.” - Mama Adi of @adizthebam
------------------------------------------------------------------
Mama Adi has embarked on her own fierce feeding journey as a mama of 3 beautiful children. Wading through the doubts and uncertainty, she found her own unique journeys with each of her kids. We celebrate you today and every day, supermama! 🦸

Mamas, it’s #TheBirthRight of you and your child to embrace your unique feeding journey. Be unabashed! Because we know you want nothing less than the best for your child. 💖

We’d love to hear about your feeding journeys below! 
.
.
